<b>Subject:</b> DUDE...get a freagin bow.<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2043" TARGET=_self>Re: My Two Cents</A> (Wangfu)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>That would wake the wretch up to be sure! In answer to the first guy's whining...I am a wizard and IF:

<P>1. A white conned warrior resists or breaks my root...I am in trouble.
<P>This happens often. Yes...I will then try ot root again...BUT...lets take a 14th level wizard.....he can do 400 hps of damage with avg resist knocking a point off here and there...and a bit of a root drain....now lets take a 14th level warrior.....hmmm don't they have close to 400 hps? The balance is there. The warrior types just have to start workin' the mages early...with a bow....once they are free they gotta start wacking the mage good (and not with a stupid two handed slow ass weapon).
<P>Last item...is goin linkdead...lets say the wizzy runs outa mana....which happens....and he runs like a woman...which happens....you prolly will lose him/her in the trees or by packet loss.....whatya do? type /exit let the game wax your foe. Suddenly you are an NPC.....OUCHY low mana wiz.
<P>Verant needs to make this AUTO attack type thing a function in game so your character will auto chase your target...and auto attack...it elimates the PACKET loss factor and suddenly a warrior type will be a real trouble maker.
<P>-Gray
<P>PS if they shorten ROOT time...wizzies ect will be impossible to play solo. If a monster even breaths on me I am dead meat. Gotta keep those bastards off me.
<P>PSSSSSS get the bow man....some bows are reaaaaaal nasty.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
